Package com.epam.aircompany.command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICommand
    Interface ICommand is an interface that will be implemented by all Command classes that process data received from JSPs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminCommand
    The Class AdminCommand processes commands from the JSP page of an administartor on which control of routes of airline is made.
    CheefCommand
    The Сlass CheefCommand processes commands from the JSP page of the director on which control of lists of employees is made.
    CreateNewEmployeeCommand
    The Сlass CreateNewEmployeeCommand processes commands from the JSP page of the director on which adding of new employees is made.
    LanguageCommand
    The Сlass LanguageCommand processes commands from the start JSP page on which is made an interface language choice
    LoginCommand
    The Class LoginCommand processes commands from the start JSP page on which authentication of the user is made.
    LogoutCommand
    The Class LogoutCommand processes commands from all JSP pages and executes completion of session of the user.
    ManagerCommand
    The Class ManagerCommand processes commands from the JSP page of the manager and executes control of crews of airplanes.
    NewRouteCommand
    The Class NewRouteCommand processes commands from the JSP page of the administrator and controls creation of a new route.
    NoCommand
    The Class NoCommand processes origin of an unknown command from the JSP page and executes transition to an application homepage.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CommandEnum
    The Enum CommandEnum commands of application.
